title: マイルCSの後に・バイブスアゲてこ

text_block_list.text: Matikanetannhauser, who unfortunately had to concede victory to Daitaku Helios. Using her frustration as a springboard, she's fired up for the next time she competes.
On her way home, she gets invited by Daitaku Helios to the 'Vibe Fest,' among other things—
And so, the 'Mile Championship' came to a close.
